name: OrderStatus
comment: Last known order status received from exchange

values.name: Sent
values.comment: Order has been sent to exchange (no response has been received yet)

values.name: Accepted
values.comment: Order has been accepted by exchange and is not yet been activated

values.name: Suspended
values.comment: Order has been suspended and requires external action to re-activate

values.name: Working
values.comment: Order is working and has not yet been completely filled

values.name: Stopped
values.comment: Order has guaranteed fill at as of yet unknown price
